a good cheltenham festival for bookies paddy power betfair was offset by bad results in second quarter as football fans backed their favourites , such as chelsea to win the premier league .
the company also said the lack of a major football tournament put a dampener on profits .
revenue for the six months to the end of june climbed 9 % to £ 827million while the operating profit climbed 22 % to £ 180m .
`` competitive pricing and promotions are essential factors behind attracting and retaining customers , '' the company said .
